name: Safer Home SH503 Indoor Plug-In Fly Trap Refill Pack of Glue Cards for SH502 Indoor Fly Trap – 3 Count (Pack of 1)
small_description: Say Goodbye to Bugs – The glue cards trap and kill flies, fruit flies, moths, gnats, and more when used with the compatible Safer Home Indoor Plug-in Fly Trap - Ideal for Your Home – These glue cards contain no synthetic insecticides and are the perfect choice for homes with children and pets - Easy to Use – Simply peel off the glue card backing and insert it into the trap. Discard and replace with a fresh glue card when it’s full of insects - Discreet and Effective – StickyTech glue cards trap and securely hold insects until time of disposal. Trapped insects are hidden on the back of the glue card, away from view - Extended Insect Protection – Includes 3 StickyTech Glue Cards to keep your Safer Home Indoor Plug-in Fly Trap up and running
full_description: With Safer Home Indoor Plug-In Fly Trap Refill Packs, you can enjoy non-stop protection from flies, fruit flies, moths, gnats, and more. Simply peel the backing off the StickyTech glue card and insert it into the trap. Plug the trap into a standard outlet near common insect hotspots, including near houseplants, exterior doors, pet areas, in kitchens, bedrooms, and other areas of your home. Once drawn in by the light of the trap, insects get stuck fast to the StickyTech Glue Cards and are securely held until the time of disposal. The unique glue placement on the wall side of the card keeps insects trapped and out of sight. StickyTech Glue Cards contain no synthetic insecticides and are the ideal choice for homes with children and pets.

name: Zevo Flying Insect Trap for Indoors: Light Trap Captures Fruit Flies, Gnats and Houseflies, Starter Kit + Refills (1 Plug-in Base + 3 Cartridges)
small_description: Zevo fly trap, fruit fly trap, and gnat trap attracts pesky flying insects in your home using specially designed blue and UV light. - Traps flying insects on a disposable adhesive backing that you never have to touch. - Removable refill cartridges available for year round protection. - Effortless 24/7 continuous attraction works day and night to help protect your family from pesky flying insects. Designed for any room or area of your home where flying insects gather including kitchens, bathrooms, garage, near plants, and living spaces. - Includes 1 plug-in base + 3 refill cartridges
full_description: The video showcases the product in use. The video guides you through product setup. The video compares multiple products. The video shows the product being unpacked. What is the Zevo Flying Insect Trap? The Zevo Flying Insect Trap features a durable plug-in base that uses blue and UV light to attract insects to a disposable refill cartridge. Insects get stuck on an adhesive pad in the cartridge, which is easy to remove and dispose of. What type of flying insects does it catch? The Zevo Flying Insect Trap is designed to catch fruit flies, gnats, house flies, drain flies, fungus gnats, & non-biting midges. Can I use the Zevo Flying Insect Trap in spaces with kids, pets and/or near food? Yes! Zevo's U.S. device base meets third-party electrical safety standards. It is a durable, plug-in base requiring 120V/60Hz power and a standard North American plug. As with other electrical devices, keep away from children. How often should I change the cartridge? Replace the refill cartridge when it is full of insects. We recommend checking it every 2 weeks or as needed. Is there anywhere you should NOT keep your trap plugged in? Do not use the Zevo Flying Insect Trap outdoors where it might get wet. Avoid placing it near TV or computer screens, and keep it away from furniture, curtains, or corners that could block insects. If you can't see Zevo, insects can't see it either.

name: INABA Churu Cat Treats, Grain-Free, Lickable, Squeezable Creamy Purée Cat Treat/Topper with Vitamin E & Taurine, 0.5 Ounces Each Tube, 50 Tubes, Tuna & Chicken Variety
small_description: MADE WITH WHOLESOME INGREDIENTS YOU CAN TRUST: Every Inaba product is made with yummy, human-grade ingredients including farm-raised chicken and/or wild-caught tuna - KEEP OUR FELINE HYDRATED WITHOUT ADDING CALORIES: Each delicious, creamy Churu tube contains 91% moisture and only 6 calories (a tenth of the calories of traditional dry cat treats), which makes it a healthy snack you can feel good about feeding - FREE OF THE BAD STUFF: Your feline friend is important to us, which is why we've kept things like grains, preservatives, artificial colors and carrageenan out of our cat treats, but we added things like Taurine to help with their overall health - HAVE THEM EATING OUT OF YOUR HAND: These lickable purée meat tubes for cats were designed to be fed by hand, as an interactive way to spend time with your feline, but you can use as a wet/dry cat food topper or as a way to disguise medication - ADD SOME VARIETY TO YOUR CAT'S LIFE: Available in eleven savory flavors, cats of all stages (kitten to senior) will be able to find a flavor they love
full_description: Here at Inaba, we know your cat is a beloved family member. That's why each of our Churu Lickable Creamy Purée Natural Cat Treats are made from high-quality ingredients, including wild-caught tuna and farm-raised chicken. Since cats are not naturally drawn to water, we have made these a high-moisture, low calorie cat treat that your kitties will love. They contain 91% moisture and have only 6 calories per tube. That's a tenth of the calories of traditional dry cat treats and more than 1000 times the moisture (8% vs. 91% moisture). In addition, we've also added Taurine to help with their vision, digestions and heart health, as well as, Vitamin E for immunity and Green Tea Extract for its natural antioxidants. What they're missing? They're grain-free, preservative-free, carrageenan-free and free from artificial colors, making them a cat treat you can feel good about feeding. Designed to be hand fed, you can use to help calm the feistiest of outdoor ferals or treat your pampered indoor pussycat. They can be used a dry/canned cat food topper or to assist with giving medications. Available in 19 savory flavors, you'll be able to find a flavor that your kitty will crave no matter what stage of life they are (kitten to senior). Inaba Churu makes snack time fun for you and your feline friends.

name: Fresh Step Clumping Cat Litter Multi-Cat Extra Strength Formula With Febreze Freshness, Multi Cat Litter With Ammonia Block Technology, 14 lb. Box
small_description: MULTI-CAT CLUMPING LITTER: Made with larger particles to keep paws and floors clean, and 99.9% dust-free while fighting litter box odors with the power of Febreze in a Fresh Scent; Packaging may vary - ODOR CONTROL MULTI-CAT LITTER: Formulated with Ammonia Block Technology, this litter has a 10-day odor control guarantee, as it controls bacterial odor growth and keeps ammonia odors away from your litter box and home - 99.9% DUST FREE LITTER: Keep surfaces cleaner and the air clearer with this low dust formula; The paw activated litter releases a Febreze freshness scent with each step your cat makes in the litter box - SCOOPABLE KITTY LITTER: Clumping litter with ClumpLock technology absorbs liquid and forms tight clumps to minimize the crumbles left behind, making clean up fast and easy - FRESH STEP CAT LITTER: Fight litter box odors with your cat’s health and happiness in mind; Certain trademarks used under license from The Procter & Gamble Company or its affiliates
full_description: Fight litter box odors in your multi-cat home with Fresh Step Multi-Cat Clumping Cat Litter. Featuring an extra-strength formula, this Fresh Step clumping cat litter delivers even more odor-fighting protection with the power of Febreze to leave behind a fresh, clean scent. This multi cat litter uses Ammonia Block technology to guarantee 10 days of odor control in your multi cat litter box (1). Featuring ClumpLock technology, the Fresh Step litter multi cat formula locks in liquid and cat urine odor on contact to form tight clumps. This makes scooping your kitty litter box quick and effortless, and it helps prevent crumbles from being left behind. In addition to easy cat litter clumping, the cat litter has a low-dust formula to help keep surfaces cleaner in your home. Enjoy more catnaps and cuddle time with your kitty when you choose Fresh Step cat litter. (1) See package for more information on terms and conditions

Blue Buffalo makes premium-quality pet foods featuring real meat, fruit, and vegetables. Love them like family. Feed them like family.

name: Earth Rated Textured Pet Wipes for Dogs & Cats, Cleaning and Odor-Controlling Grooming Wipes for Paws, Body, and Butt, Unscented, 100 Count
small_description: HIGH-QUALITY PET WIPES: These textured wipes are the perfect everyday cleaning solution for your pet's paws, body, and butt. Unscented, they keep your dog or cat smelling fresh and clean. - GENTLE INGREDIENTS: These pet wipes contain high-quality ingredients like soothing aloe, shea butter, chamomile, and cucumber. They are perfect for cleaning your dog after walks, hikes, or in between baths. - USER FRIENDLY: Made of thick, durable, USDA Certified 99% Biobased material, our plant-based pet wipes have just the right amount of moisture for an effective clean every time. - A BETTER WIPE: Our pet wipes are hypoallergenic, cruelty-free, dermatologist-tested, and free of alcohol and parabens. Each wipe measures 8" L x 8" W. These pet wipes are not flushable. - EARTH RATED: Our mission is to make everyday moments for people and their dogs simpler and better. We do this by designing innovative products that are thoughtfully unexpected. We are also proudly B Corp Certified.
full_description: 1 Gentle Ingredients 2 Soft and Durable 3 Gentle Clean 4 For Daily Grooming What’s your mission? Our mission is to make everyday moments for people and their dogs simpler and better. We do this by designing innovative products that are thoughtfully-unexpected. Why choose Earth Rated? In 2009, we set out to encourage responsible dog-ownership by creating poop bags and a dispenser that made picking up less of a chore. Today, as a B Corp certified company, we integrate environmental and social considerations into everything we do. What can I use dog wipes for? Our wipes are perfect for quick cleanups of paws, face, body & bum. They’re soft, large (8x8 in), & made of plant-based material that is Certified USDA 99% Biobased. They’re hypoallergenic, free of alcohol & parabens, & gentle enough for daily use. Are your wipes flushable? Our wipes should not be flushed as we have not specifically tested the impact that this might have on your system. Are your wipes cruelty-free? Absolutely. Our wipes are cruelty-free and Leaping Bunny certified. Find the right wipes for your dog.
